line_1: "Ha!" quoth the Miller, moved at speech so rash,
line_2: "Art thou like me? then where thy notes and cash?

line_1: While the vex'd parent rails at deed so rash,
line_2: Shall d — n his luck, and stretch his hand for cash.

line_2: Will with your virtue, peace, or interest, clash;
